<span></span></div><div>Going to add my own story to this.

Me: Son, I'm trans.
Him (8 at the time): Really?

Me: Really.

Him: Really Really??

Me (on the edge of tears, barely holding it together, fearful of what his reaction might be): Yes, I'm a woman.

Him: ...

Me: I want you to know I'll always love you.

Him (deep in thought): ...

Me (tears rolling now): Do... do you have any questions?

Him: ... will I be let off my chores?
Me: No, you still need to empty the dishwasher.

Him: ... will I get extra candy?
Me: No, you having two mommies doesn't get you more candy.

Wife (nods firmly at the no-extra-candy rule)
Me: Do you have any more questions?
Him: ...can I tell you about the movie I just saw with grandma?

Me: Any questions about me being trans.
Him: So I use she and her for you now like for other girls?

Me: Yes.
Him: OK... I love you mommy. Anyway... grandmapickedmeupfromschool. WewenttothemoviesandgotpopcornandIhadawholethingofitand (pause for breath) thereisthiskidcalledBillyBatsonbuthebecomesSHAZAM! (pause for breath) andhefightsdemonsandtherewasawizardheisplayedbythe (pause for breath) guyfromchuckwhoplayschuckyouknowthespyand (pause for breath) hischestlightsupandhehaslightningandissuperstrongbutnotascoolatheFlash...</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tuaAIzM</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ThatOtherGirlYouKnow]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Unreal</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9IyhKLc</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Qp7zFpl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Tweet link .https://twitter.com/nytimes/status/1508476529214435334</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9IyhKLc</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mech0T1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Neat!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/QeTRNlk</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Io81tOF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cUHn39O.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/b7WADKg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BFcipEX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uD7bAsv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Artist: Alex Colville 

